00:29:05,000 --> 00:29:07,000
 Then right after that, she got pregnant.

460
00:29:07,000 --> 00:29:10,000
 She's like, wow, God, you're bringing beauty from ashes.

461
00:29:10,000 --> 00:29:16,000
 Then her husband has pretty intense surgery and then she has a miscarriage.

462
00:29:16,000 --> 00:29:21,000
 And then her husband has complications from the surgery.

463
00:29:21,000 --> 00:29:27,000
 She has to drive him to the ER while miscarrying their baby.

464
00:29:27,000 --> 00:29:33,000
 For the past two years, she said, Tyler, I've gone through incredible pain.

