00:29:50,000 --> 00:29:55,000
 She said, Tyler, as I've been pouring myself out before God, here's been my

469
00:29:55,000 --> 00:29:56,000
 prayer.

470
00:29:56,000 --> 00:30:01,000
 My prayer has been, God, override my heart and give me your desire.

471
00:30:01,000 --> 00:30:06,000
 She said this, I want my guts to match yours.

472
00:30:06,000 --> 00:30:09,000
 Who prays like that?

473
00:30:09,000 --> 00:30:11,000
 You know who prays like that?

474
00:30:11,000 --> 00:30:14,000
 It's somebody who's been through the fire.

