00:30:19,000 --> 00:30:22,000
 Instead turns it to, God, what are you doing in me?

477
00:30:22,000 --> 00:30:24,000
 What are you doing?

478
00:30:24,000 --> 00:30:28,000
 And all of a sudden, you begin to pray like this book.

