00:37:40,000 --> 00:37:42,000
 "I can deal with who you really are.

637
00:37:42,000 --> 00:37:45,000
 "I can't deal with this fake mess that you're pulling off

638
00:37:45,000 --> 00:37:47,000
 "with showing up this way and this way and this way.

639
00:37:47,000 --> 00:37:49,000
 "You just gotta be real."

